        dc:description           "Figures 15 - 19. Pampsilota dahomeyanus: 15. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 16. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 17. Lancet; 18. Serrulae 10 - 11; 19. Penis valve (left, lateral aspect)." , "Figure 37. Distribution map for Pampsilota leleupi, Pampsilota luederitzensis, Pampsilota nigeriae, Pampsilota tsavoensis, and Pampsilota zebra." , "Figures 66 - 71. Pampsilota tsavoensis ♀ (HT), dorsal / lateral. 68 - 71. Pampsilota zebra. 68 - 69 ♀ (HT), dorsal / lateral; 70 - 71. ♂ (PT), dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 27 - 30. Pampsilota tsavoensis: 27. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 28. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 29. Lancet; 30. Serrulae 10 - 11." ;
